Following reactions from people over the reality TV show featured by Nigerian singer, Innocent Idibia, popularly known as 2Baba and his wife, Annie Idibia, the singer has revealed why he loves her as his African queen. Recall that Annie has been under attack on social media over some the statements she made during the Netflix reality show, titled “Young, Famous & African”. However, 2Baba in a post on Instagram expressed that one of the reasons he loves Annie is because of her honest nature. He wrote, “I’ve never been a fan of all this reality TV thing but I must ask or rather point out. The fact that whatever Annie felt, she said it straight up to whoever. She never laughed with anybody and say different behind. “That is one of the reasons I love this African queen.”